<br><b>DefineViewTables</b> page allows to select which columns and in which order will be displayed in Persons/Samples/Aliquots pages.
To change the settings, enter numbers of columns (starting from 1) in which the fields of interest should be displayed.
Column number <i>0</i> means that the corresponding field will not be displayed. 
<br>
<br>One of the intended uses for filed selection is for generation of reports. Select the fields which you wish to
see in report (and in which order), then go to Persons/Samples/Aliquots pages and export the date from this page by
clicking on "Export" tab. Data will be saved in tab-delimited format.
<br>
<br>Display settings are preserved only within the current session. After the next login the default settings will be restored.
